{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"8a6coxxsai40bn2skue8q1l","title":"Under a Vast Sky|海闊天空","desc":"","updated":1653364693842,"created":1653363788457,"custom":{},"fname":"extra.underavastsky","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"802536f47d2c089d0f0204ca7dae719f","links":[{"from":{"fname":"extra","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":4,"offset":229},"end":{"line":7,"column":27,"offset":252},"indent":[]},"value":"extra.underavastsky","alias":"extra.underavastsky"}],"anchors":{"lyrics":{"type":"header","text":"Lyrics:","value":"lyrics","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"official-video":{"type":"header","text":"Official Video","value":"official-video","line":60,"column":0,"depth":2},"under-a-vast-sky---defence-of-cuhk":{"type":"header","text":"\"Under a Vast Sky\" - Defence of CUHK:","value":"under-a-vast-sky---defence-of-cuhk","line":64,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"dr6y9n9s72kljfnr7bpwvqj","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"under-a-vast-sky海闊天空\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#under-a-vast-sky海闊天空\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Under a Vast Sky|海闊天空</h1>\n<p>\"Under a Vast Sky\" (海闊天空) is a song written and recorded by the once phenomenal band - Beyond. The song was widely sung during the Umbrella Movement in 2014 as well as the Anti-ELAB (Anti-Extradition Law Amendment Bill) Movement in 2019, due to its theme about love of freedom and ideals.</p>\n<h2 id=\"lyrics\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#lyrics\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Lyrics:</h2>\n<p>今天我　寒夜裡看雪飄過\n懷著冷卻了的心窩漂遠方\n風雨裏追趕\n霧裡分不清影蹤\n天空海闊你與我\n可會變(誰沒在變)</p>\n<p>多少次　迎著冷眼與嘲笑\n從沒有放棄過心中的理想\n一剎那恍惚\n若有所失的感覺\n不知不覺已變淡\n心裡愛(誰明白我)</p>\n<p>原諒我這一生不羈放縱愛自由\n也會怕有一天會跌倒\n背棄了理想　誰人都可以\n那會怕有一天只你共我</p>\n<p>今天我　寒夜裡看雪飄過\n懷著冷卻了的心窩漂遠方\n風雨裏追趕\n霧裡分不清影蹤\n天空海闊你與我\n可會變(誰沒在變)</p>\n<p>原諒我這一生不羈放縱愛自由\n也會怕有一天會跌倒\n背棄了理想　誰人都可以\n那會怕有一天只你共我</p>\n<p>仍然自由自我\n永遠高唱我歌走遍千里</p>\n<p>原諒我這一生不羈放縱愛自由\n也會怕有一天會跌倒\n背棄了理想　誰人都可以\n那會怕有一天只你共我</p>\n<p>背棄了理想　誰人都可以\n那會怕有一天只你共我</p>\n<p>原諒我這一生不羈放縱愛自由\n也會怕有一天會跌倒\n背棄了理想　誰人都可以\n那會怕有一天只你共我</p>\n<h2 id=\"official-video\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#official-video\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Official Video</h2>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qu_FSptjRic\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<h2 id=\"under-a-vast-sky---defence-of-cuhk\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#under-a-vast-sky---defence-of-cuhk\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>\"Under a Vast Sky\" - Defence of CUHK:</h2>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Swxhubp82ds\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/dr6y9n9s72kljfnr7bpwvqj\">Extra</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","title":"SHKO(Save Hong Kong Online)","desc":"","updated":1650946407329,"created":1648525691085,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"2b86c1076b19a68a88243e5002a6b2cb","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"pfy4h1nwep9age7eg0u8xe1","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"background","alias":"the vast disappearing of civil society and independent media","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":129,"offset":346},"end":{"line":5,"column":206,"offset":423},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"background"}},{"type